name: Khaya Luxury Villa by Nagisa Bali
address: Jalan Bukit Damai, Banjar Sawangan ,Nusa Dua, Kutuh, Kec. Kuta Sel., Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80361, Indonesia
review 1:
It's a nice villa with a spectacular view down to the ocean. Loads of space with 4 very comfortable double bedrooms. Some of the bathrooms are a bit quirky, with baths and showers outdoors, which wasn't totally practical in rain and wind [although just bad luck with the weather I guess].

The villa deserves 5 stars, but it really needs a good professional clean and some maintenance - the kitchen particularly needs it. Things are sticky, cupboards and drawers need fixing or replacing, and the equipment needs replacing.

It is obviously a popular and well used holiday spot, so the owners would do well to take a few weeks to get the place back up into top-top shape again.
review 2: Very nice private villa ideal for family visiting bali. Exquisite views. Awesome staff
review 3: Beautiful property and view. Very relaxing. Just far a away from anything
review 4:
Nice villa
Good staff Pak Made and Ibu Ella is super helpful
